43
00:06:26,696 --> 00:06:27,890
One moment.

44
00:06:37,574 --> 00:06:39,838
Follow the signs to Sector C.

45
00:07:19,816 --> 00:07:20,874
I got it.

46
00:07:22,018 --> 00:07:25,146
Fifty-nine. There are three doors,
so it should be...

47
00:07:26,256 --> 00:07:28,486
Let's see. It's this...

48
00:07:28,558 --> 00:07:30,719
How'd you know that?

49
00:07:30,794 --> 00:07:33,786
He's so smart. This kid of ours is so smart.

50
00:07:34,331 --> 00:07:36,458
How'd you know it was that door?

51
00:07:36,633 --> 00:07:38,225
Tie your shoelaces.

52
00:07:39,836 --> 00:07:40,962
I'll do it.

53
00:07:41,104 --> 00:07:43,299
Are you sure this is the right door?

54
00:07:51,481 --> 00:07:52,743
