184
00:21:50,786 --> 00:21:52,947
- What are you doing?
- Running away.

185
00:21:53,122 --> 00:21:54,714
What are you running from?

186
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:56,223
The bad people.

187
00:21:56,892 --> 00:21:58,450
The bad people?

188
00:21:59,295 --> 00:22:01,024
Come, we'll take you home.

189
00:22:05,301 --> 00:22:07,292
- Your folks in the military?
- No.

190
00:22:08,404 --> 00:22:10,235
Sector C, Petey.

191
00:22:44,773 --> 00:22:46,240
There's my bike!

192
00:22:46,308 --> 00:22:48,833
That's your bike? Okay, pull it over.

193
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:06,121
Sure this is the house?

194
00:23:10,466 --> 00:23:11,956
What's going on?

195
00:23:12,801 --> 00:23:14,291
Found him wandering around.

196
00:23:14,370 --> 00:23:15,962
We figured he was lost.

197
00:23:18,874 --> 00:23:20,603
You should be in day care.

198
00:23:20,709 --> 00:23:22,370
I hate that place.

199
00:23:22,811 --> 00:23:23,835
What happened?

200
00:23:23,913 --> 00:23:25,904
They all had the same pictures.

201
00:23:26,882 --> 00:23:29,476
They tried to make me go to sleep.

202
00:23:29,885 --> 00:23:32,376
Tried to make me go to sleep.

203
00:23:34,823 --> 00:23:36,950
Sorry to have troubled you.

204
00:23:37,393 --> 00:23:38,485
No trouble.

205
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:40,221
What're you doing home?

206
00:23:40,296 --> 00:23:42,457
Are you an MP, or something?

207
00:23:43,165 --> 00:23:45,326
No, I'm a chopper pilot.

208
00:23:46,568 --> 00:23:48,559
Thanks for bringing him home.

209
00:23:50,172 --> 00:23:51,901
Maybe I'll see you around.

210
00:23:53,075 --> 00:23:53,905
Where?

211
00:23:57,846 --> 00:24:01,009
Top Gun? It's on Route 8.
It's the only club around.

212
00:24:01,917 --> 00:24:03,407
Name's Tim.

213
00:24:05,254 --> 00:24:06,585
Marti.

214
00:24:10,859 --> 00:24:12,520
- No problem at all.
- Thanks.

215
00:24:12,594 --> 00:24:13,754
Take care.

216
00:24:15,764 --> 00:24:17,197
- Thank you.
- No problem.

217
00:24:17,266 --> 00:24:18,528
Appreciate it.

218
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:20,363
Thanks very much.

219
00:24:20,769 --> 00:24:22,361
All right. Take care.

220
00:24:22,438 --> 00:24:24,599
- Say, "Thank you."
- Thank you.

221
00:24:29,278 --> 00:24:33,112
What's this about, "The kids don't
