223
00:24:36,552 --> 00:24:39,646
The faster he goes back,
the faster he'll make friends.

224
00:24:51,633 --> 00:24:52,964
- Hi.
- Hey, chick.

225
00:24:53,235 --> 00:24:55,135
Get your coat. Let's go.

226
00:24:56,171 --> 00:24:57,331
Where are we going?

227
00:24:57,406 --> 00:25:00,068
Out. Anywhere. Anywhere but here.

228
00:25:01,977 --> 00:25:04,138
Jenn Platt, Carol.

229
00:25:06,248 --> 00:25:09,308
I'm sorry, I didn't realize you knew...
Steve!

230
00:25:09,485 --> 00:25:11,680
Marti has a friend here. Want anything?

231
00:25:11,754 --> 00:25:13,881
- We don't have much.
- I'm fine.

232
00:25:13,956 --> 00:25:15,753
We have milk, orange juice...

233
00:25:16,025 --> 00:25:17,686
I could make lemonade. Or tea.

234
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:18,988
We have mint.

235
00:25:19,094 --> 00:25:21,528
- Jenn Platt. Nice to meet you.
- Steve Malone.

236
00:25:21,597 --> 00:25:22,586
Popcorn?

237
00:25:23,165 --> 00:25:25,258
- I'm fine.
- Did you say "Platt"?

238
00:25:25,334 --> 00:25:27,097
Yes, the general's daughter.

239
00:25:27,669 --> 00:25:30,433
I came by to take Marti
and show her around.

240
00:25:31,774 --> 00:25:32,763
Where?

241
00:25:33,609 --> 00:25:36,009
The base. The rec center.

242
00:25:37,012 --> 00:25:39,173
When are you planning to be home?

243
00:25:39,848 --> 00:25:40,940
12:00?

244
00:25:46,688 --> 00:25:47,780
Done! Let's go.

245
00:25:48,190 --> 00:25:52,251
But do be home by 12:00. That's all I ask.
Just be home by 12:00.

246
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:53,452
Nice meeting you.

247
00:25:53,529 --> 00:25:56,293
That's a really interesting outfit
you've got on.

248
00:26:00,436 --> 00:26:02,267
- Here?
- This is it.

249
00:26:03,539 --> 00:26:05,302
I don't have any ID.

250
00:26:05,874 --> 00:26:08,809
Don't get your panties in a bunch.
Just come.

251
00:26:21,890 --> 00:26:24,381
Oh, man, where is everybody?

252
00:26:25,994 --> 00:26:27,723
Hey, ladies.

253
00:26:27,996 --> 00:26:29,657
You want to dance?

254
00:26:29,898 --> 00:26:31,160
Lambada?

255
00:26:36,171 --> 00:26:37,729
Look who's here.

256
00:26:37,906 --> 00:26:39,897
I don't believe my eyes. Jenn.

257
00:26:39,975 --> 00:26:42,910
Where is everybody?
Word get out that you'd be here?

258
00:26:43,078 --> 00:26:45,103
They heard your old man was coming.

259
00:26:45,180 --> 00:26:47,341
Yeah, to court-martial your ass.

260
00:26:47,516 --> 00:26:50,007
- This is Pete and...
- Marti.

261
00:26:50,586 --> 00:26:52,076
You know each other?

262
00:26:52,421 --> 00:26:53,854
We met earlier.

263
00:26:54,089 --> 00:26:56,523
When? You just got here yesterday.

264
00:26:58,594 --> 00:27:00,357
What do I do to get a drink here?

265
00:27:00,429 --> 00:27:02,420
You want a drink? Have a drink.

266
